Program: The Why Factor
Title: World War One: National Pride
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p021l9tz
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 30 Jun 2014
In this edition of The Why Factor Mike Williams explores national pride. Why are we so drawn to symbols of statehood, and how can leaders use that loyalty? Today, a flying flag, a rousing speech and an anthem - a national anthem. Produced by Ben Crighton & Laura Gray (Image of a military band playing brass instruments. Credit: Shutterstock) Show less